	\'95	Isaiah 50:11 \'96 \'93All you who light fires and provide yourselves with flaming torches, walk in the light of your fires\'85 this you will receive from My hand: you will lie down in torment.\'94\
\
What Is False Light in the OT?\
	\'95	Self-Made Wisdom: Attempting to generate spiritual insight apart from God\'92s revelation.\
	\'95	Idolatry as Enlightenment: Worshipping created things as though they bring illumination.\
	\'95	Misplaced Glory: Seeking honor without submission to God\'92s design.\
\
False Light in the Garden:\
	\'95	Genesis 3:5: \'93You will be like God, knowing good and evil.\'94\
	\'95	The Serpent\'92s Lie: A promise of knowledge without submission to God.\
\
